sec.p:
Applying mathematical models to optimize energy flows within VECs in Bulgaria can contribute to more efficient use of local resources and a reduction in energy dependence. A basic mathematical approach is illustrated by the following formula:
\begin{equation*}
\text { Minimize } C=\sum_{t=1}^{T}\left(C_{\text {gen }}(t)+C_{\text {stor }}(t)+C_{\text {exch }}(t)\right)
\tag{1}
\end{equation*}
